<h4>Global Settings</h4>
<ul>
<li> Option to enable or disable Checkout plugin. </li>
<li> Option to select the checkout style type.</li>
<li> Option to set the tab alignment in the Centre, Left, or in Right.</li>
<li> Option to change the label for Login, Billing, Shipping, Order info,and Payment.</li>
<li><strong>New:</strong> Option to combine the Billing and Shipping details.</li>
</ul>

